```javascript
function coinChangeWays(amount, coins) {
  const dp = new Array(amount + 1).fill(0);
  dp[0] = 1;
  for (const c of coins) {
    for (let a = c; a <= amount; a++) dp[a] += dp[a - c];
  }
  return dp[amount];
}
```

**Time**: O(n * amount). **Space**: O(amount) — collapsed from the 2-D table.

